{"tid":339831,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"又食返煙","createTime":"2017-07-29T11:36:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T12:49:15.000Z","uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"968eab00fe7f2c38a94fa12cdd3f69f6d975965d","tid":339831,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:36:09.000Z","msg":"個時拍拖 大家都話決定一齊介 話想健康d 希望可以白頭到老 唔想另一個早死 但依家佢唔係我身邊 我諗依個承諾都唔洗守啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原本依包係薄荷煙黎 但放左係度太耐 無哂薄荷味 得返淡淡既苦澀味 唔知係包煙變質 定係我個心覺得好苦<br />\n<br />\n隨著火機拍的一聲把快樂燃點 隨著風中花飛煙圈消散我亦明白應怎打算<br />\n<br />\n唔知係我點依支煙既同時 會唔會有人係世界上某角落 都係點起一支煙 會諗起我呢？"},{"pid":"f1f461fecd5f448d836e3a2a560f77c81b0ab916","tid":339831,"uid":20363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:36:52.000Z","msg":"食煙自己喱埋死啦唔好害人"},{"pid":"110fbcb142154ec886c1683906690e0dac97e073","tid":339831,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:40:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c4f144b2959ecb6d7f005c6c65713117323388","tid":339831,"uid":110243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:42:47.000Z","msg":"每次聽借火都好想食"},{"pid":"cf37eda4e4f741d14b45d5a64b8ab0ed2ccde3fc","tid":339831,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食煙自己喱埋死啦唔好害人</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5e0da42dd5dd107cd58184b0a253617d645ef85e","tid":339831,"uid":38884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:49:15.000Z","msg":"momo唔鐘意人食煙"}]}